descript.abstract: Line coverage extracting from the travel_route coverage to display of the George Washington and Jefferson National Forests Transportation (Trail) system. The coverage includes Forest Trails, Major Federal and State Trails.
descript.purpose: To maintain and inventory Trail Transportation System on the George Washington and Jefferson National Forests.
descript.supplinf: Digital data capture is by manual digitizing which carries inherent precision and accuracy limitations. The data may not meet National Map Accuracy Standards.
